ActFederal Public Sector Labour Relations Act
SubjectNational Film Board - Canadian Union of Public Employees, Local 2656 ** Collective Agreement **
PrecisOrder approving that the National Film Board ENTER INTO A COLLECTIVE AGREEMENT with the Canadian Union of Public Employees, Local 2656, in respect of its employees in the Administrative Support category and the Operational category, which agreement is from July 1, 2018 to June 30, 2022.
